Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格尼做的咖喱面包很有营养的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了之后一定要笑口常开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很烫的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏尔他…夏尔他失去记忆了
