Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:04.52,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}此処には無いと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kakeyotta senaka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.34,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}駆け寄った背中に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}toikakeru ashita ga donna katachi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.54,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}問いかける明日がどんあ形でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}yuruga nakatta no wa mou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.57,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}揺るがなかったのはもう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:27.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}shinjiru koto wo wasuretaku nakatta kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:27.29,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}信じる事を忘れたくなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:35.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}me wo sorasu kuse mo aimai na taido mo waraenu uso mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:35.70,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}目を逸らす癖も 曖昧な回答も 笑えぬ嘘も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:42.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tonari ni inakereba ima sae nijin de yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:42.97,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}隣に居なければ意味さえ 滲んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.67,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}たとえ終わる事の無い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.67,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tatoe owaru koto no nai
